Advantages of SCD Type 2 ⭐⭐⭐

1. Full Historical Tracking

Most important advantage.
---

2. Accurate Historical Reporting
Past reports remain correct.
---
3. Audit Compliance

Critical for finance/banking.
---

4. Customer Journey Analysis
Track behavior evolution.
---

Disadvantages ⚠️

1. Increased Storage
Rows continuously grow.
---
2. More Complex ETL
Need change detection logic.
---

3. Query Complexity
Need current-record filtering.
---

Important Interview Insight ⭐
Type 2 is preferred when business history matters.
This line is extremely important.
---

