Notes Version

# SCD Type 2

## Definition
Preserves historical changes by inserting new rows.

## Key Idea
Do not overwrite old data.

## Common Columns
- effective_date
- end_date
- is_current

## Why Surrogate Key?
Allows multiple records for same business key.

## Advantages
- Full history
- Accurate reporting
- Audit support

## Disadvantages
- More storage
- Complex ETL
- Complex queries
